object.customQuery:
SELECT Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_ID, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Code, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Name, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Contact_Phone, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Contact_Fax, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Address, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_City, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_State, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Zipcode, Master_Agency_Detail.Sales_Territory, Master_Agency_Detail.Field_Representative_State, Master_Agency_Detail.Field_Representative, Master_Agency_Detail.Field_Representative_Group, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Email1, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Email2, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Email3, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Email4, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Email5, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Email6, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Email7, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Email8, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Email9, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Email10, Master_Agency_Detail.Source_Cd, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Appointed_Dt, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Mail_Address1, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Mail_Address2, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Mail_City, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Mail_State, Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Mail_Zipcode, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.Agency_Group_Id, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.Agency_Group_Nbr, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.Agency_Group_Name, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.Agency_Group_Name1, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.Agency_Group_Name2, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.Qualifying_Amount, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.AgencyGroup_Email1, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.AgencyGroup_Email2, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.AgencyGroup_Email3, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.AgencyGroup_Email4, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.AgencyGroup_Email5, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.AgencyGroup_Email6, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.AgencyGroup_Email7, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.AgencyGroup_Email8, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.AgencyGroup_Email9, Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.AgencyGroup_Email10, Master_Agency_Detail.Status, Master_Agency_Detail.agency_alpha_workflow 
FROM
dbo.Master_Agency_Detail Master_Agency_Detail 
 LEFT JOIN dbo.Master_AgencyGroup_Detail Master_AgencyGroup_Detail 
 ON Master_Agency_Detail.Agency_Group_Nbr = Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.Agency_Group_Nbr
 WHERE Master_Agency_Detail.Row_End_Dt > GETDATE()
 and Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.Row_End_Dt > GETDATE()
AND (Master_Agency_Detail.row_effective_dt >= (SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_subquery_tables')
or Master_AgencyGroup_Detail.row_effective_dt >= (SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_subquery_tables'))
